## Ecosystem Integration and Workflow

Amplitude products integrate seamlessly to provide end-to-end analytics and optimization workflows. Analytics data informs experiment design and audience creation, while experiment results feed back into analytics for comprehensive impact analysis. Session Replay provides qualitative context for quantitative insights, and Guides and Surveys enable direct user feedback collection based on behavioral triggers.

The platform supports both technical and business users through role-based access controls, with developers accessing SDKs and APIs while business users leverage the web interface for analysis and campaign management. Cross-product data sharing ensures consistent user identification and behavioral tracking across all Amplitude products.

**Partner Integrations** extend platform capabilities through third-party connections, enabling data sharing with marketing automation, customer support, and business intelligence tools.

**Migration Support** assists organizations transitioning from other analytics platforms, providing data mapping guidance and implementation best practices to ensure continuity of insights and analysis capabilities.